column2: SELECT TOP #   x.objID AS xObjID,pz.objID AS pzObjID, p.objID AS pObjID, s.specObjID, s.bestObjID, g.specObjID AS gSpecObjID FROM MyDB.FIRST_RADec_Half AS f   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x   JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON x.objID = p.objID   JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID   JOIN Photoz pz ON x.objID = pz.objID   JOIN galSpecLine g ON s.bestObjID = g.specObjID
